dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents buildings for Dane County, Wisconsin in YE2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Dane_Buildings_YE2016.gdb. [This dataset contains building polygon data for Dane County. The dataset consists of structures the size of a single car garage or larger for Dane County, WI excluding structures within the City of Madison. In the City of Madison, building polygons are included for structures the size of a duplex or larger, except for around the Isthmus area.]
uw_supplemental_s: For complete metadata documentation, please visit https://lio.countyofdane.com/This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2017. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2016. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2017.
